Importing OmniStudio for Vlocity DataPacks into OmniStudio orgs is supported, however importing OmniStudio DataPacks into OmniStudio for Vlocity orgs isn't supported. 

You must add NASA as a Remote Site and get an API key to create this example Integration Procedure, which retrieves the astronomy picture of the day from NASA using NASA's publicly available REST API.
